| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1455 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2f214dfb-bcf3-5482-9d0f-711d97f91a4b"
